(4, 1, '2012-01-16 16:16:35', '2012-01-16 16:16:35', 'Built by <a href="https://www.trovster.com">Trevor Morris</a>, designed by <a href="https://www.aarontolley.co.uk">Aaron Tolley</a>, and run by an army of thinkers, Design + Hype strive to bring you the most creative content from across the web. Ranging from interesting  <a href="/typography/">Typography</a> and <a href="/illustration/">Illustrations</a> to inspiring <a href="/websites/">Websites</a> and stunning <a href="/photography/">Photography</a>.\r\n\r\nAaron Tolley is a freelance graphic designer from just outside Birmingham, he has been designing websites and printed material as well as creating brands and graphic identities since 2005.  Trevor Morris, freelancing as ''Surface'', is a website developer specialising in bespoke Wordpress development and responsive website design. He has been building high-end online solutions for over 15 years.\r\n\r\nIf you wish to share something with us please send us an email to <a href="mailto:hello@designandhype.com">hello@designandhype.com</a>. Maybe you''ve found something we would love, maybe you''ve just created a masterpiece and want to show the World? Don''t be shy, send it over.', 'About this site', 'Showcasing only the best creative design from across the web. Design + Hype is your new go-to site for design inspiration.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2012-01-24 19:40:40', '2012-01-24 19:40:40', '', 0, 'http://http://www.designandhype.com/?page_id=4', 10, 'page', '', 0),
