(689, 11, '2012-06-25 17:41:30', '2012-06-25 17:41:30', 'With last year''s extraordinary <a title="See No Evil" href="http://www.seenoevilbristol.co.uk" target="_blank">See No Evil</a> event transforming a once-grimy Bristol city centre street, this year’s event promises to be even better. The council finally stopped ignoring street art as an integral part of Bristol''s creative hub to allow this event to take place. With last month’s Upfest only slightly dampened by the rain the weekend of 16th-19th August is a date for the diary. Here are a few pictures of last year’s See No Evil to remind you what it''s all about; this year they are promising ''more art, more music, more diversity''.', 'See No Evil Returns In August', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'see-no-evil-returns-in-august', '', '', '2012-06-25 17:41:30', '2012-06-25 17:41:30', '', 0, 'http://www.designandhype.com/?p=689', 0, 'post', '', 0),
